---
const EMAIL = 'maximebouger.freelance@gmail.com';
const CALENDLY = 'CALENDLY_LINK';
---
<section class="bg-gray-900/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-800/50 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors duration-300 h-100 text-center">
  <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-semibold">Prêt à diagnostiquer vos freins techniques ?</h3>
  <p class="mt-2 text-slate-200">Audit express 1j — rapport synthétique + 3 quick wins.</p>

  <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center gap-3">

      <button
              onclick={`Calendly.initPopupWidget({url:'https://calendly.com/${CALENDLY}'});return false;`}
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2  bg-gradient-from-blue border-purple-500/50 text-base font-medium rounded-xl text-white hover:bg-purple-500/10 transition-all duration-300"
      >

          Réserver un créneau
      </button>

    <a class="px-4 py-3 rounded-md border" href={`mailto:${EMAIL}`}>
      Me contacter
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
